{
  "stem": "3933.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We ran to-- we went in the evening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was living with his sister and his brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Kola was living with his sister and his brother-in-law, with a little boy who was my son's age.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we came there, you can imagine how I could spend the night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They weren't crazy about seeing me, for two reasons-- because I'm-- they're anti-Semites, obviously, automatically.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And secondly, it was a danger to hide the Jews, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He did it for his feelings for me, was a different picture-- not for his being so sentimental or being so loyal or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now over the night it was-- well I'll never this night-- forget the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the morning, the woman came into the living in the middle because in East European countries you deliver the-- deliver the milk every morning in a big-- in a big aluminum can but, well, whatever.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she said, did you hear?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you hear?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did you hear, they pinched out the Jews-- they two of them lying when even-- when I walked, she said, I saw two of them lying.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said they were running and they shot after them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They came in with trucks and they picked, pulled them, put them into the trucks and they drove away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, oh, my God, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She still is alive-- I think she is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I send to-- to him in a package.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She lives in a city, you know what the name of the city?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Auschwitz-- coincidence.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nice name of a city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Her husband, second husband came from there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I hear Lucia saying, oh, my God.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Yannick, which is her husband's name, Yannick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not the second one-- he was also killed by Germans, by the way, a coincidence.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
